or Luo Ailian?

13
00:01:44,592 --> 00:01:45,432
Nonsense.

14
00:01:45,792 --> 00:01:47,152
Those who died can't cause any trouble.

15
00:01:51,712 --> 00:01:52,391
Ghost.

16
00:01:53,152 --> 00:01:53,872
Ghost.

17
00:01:54,952 --> 00:01:55,792
She's back.

18
00:01:56,232 --> 00:01:56,872
She's haunting.

19
00:01:57,751 --> 00:01:59,031
Calm down!

20
00:02:01,512 --> 00:02:02,592
Master got frightened,

21
00:02:02,592 --> 00:02:03,831
saying nonsense to scare the guests.

22
00:02:04,311 --> 00:02:05,751
Let's get him down to rest.

23
00:02:05,751 --> 00:02:06,391
Ghost.

24
00:02:06,992 --> 00:02:07,592
Ghost.

25
00:02:12,072 --> 00:02:13,072
Miss Shen.

26
00:02:13,912 --> 00:02:15,312
I'm really sorry strange things

27
00:02:15,352 --> 00:02:16,111
