The goods haven't
even left the Luo residence.

41
00:02:53,192 --> 00:02:54,312
How dare you take the money!

42
00:02:55,591 --> 00:02:56,512
Rules are rules,

43
00:02:56,591 --> 00:02:57,472
but we can be flexible.

44
