This deal was voided
before it even got started.

45
00:03:00,032 --> 00:03:01,512
So it's not breaking the rules.

46
00:03:01,952 --> 00:03:03,312
What do you think, Miss Shen?

47
00:03:03,912 --> 00:03:04,591
Guards!

48
00:03:17,912 --> 00:03:19,151
Strange things keep happening here.

49
00:03:19,151 --> 00:03:20,472
And now you break the promise

50
00:03:20,472 --> 00:03:22,591
and want to play

51
00:03:22,591 --> 00:03:23,671
the bully.

52
00:03:23,671 --> 00:03:25,352
You might be laughed at
if word gets out.

53
00:03:25,752 --> 00:03:27,991
Who would know what happens

54
00:03:28,512 --> 00:03:30,271
in the Luo's Residence?

55
00:03:35,391 --> 00:03:36,391
What do you want to do?

56
00:03:36,912 --> 00:03:38,391
Just the two of you,

57
00:03:38,431 --> 00:03:41,032
