58
00:03:42,551 --> 00:03:43,591
How do you know

59
00:03:44,072 --> 00:03:45,352
it's just the two of us?

60
00:03:47,991 --> 00:03:49,192
Even if all of your armed escorts

61
00:03:49,192 --> 00:03:50,632
came to your rescue, so what?

62
00:03:51,151 --> 00:03:52,591
Do you think we would be afraid?

63
00:03:52,752 --> 00:03:54,111
Why don't you send someone

64
00:03:54,111 --> 00:03:55,752
to the alley out there to find out?

65
00:04:02,271 --> 00:04:03,632
Mother, don't waste our time.

66
00:04:03,952 --> 00:04:05,072
Just go get the money.

67
00:04:06,312 --> 00:04:09,312
You wretch! How dare you fool us!

68
00:04:09,312 --> 00:04:10,312
Give the money back.

69
00:04:15,192 --> 00:04:15,831
Who dares to move?

70
00:04:15,831 --> 00:04:16,391
Nobody moves.

71
00:04:16,391 --> 00:04:17,512
Mother, she hit me.

72
00:04:19,151 --> 00:04:20,432
I'm really sorry.

73
00:04:20,632 --> 00:04:22,192
I've learned the martial arts,

74
00:04:22,192 --> 00:04:23,471
so it's just my natural reaction.

75
00:04:30,591 --> 00:04:32,151
Madam, Miss Shuangshuang.

76
00:04:32,672 --> 00:04:33,632
Those armed escorts

77
00:04:33,791 --> 00:04:35,192
