78
00:04:35,192 --> 00:04:36,471
at the sight of us.

79
00:04:36,752 --> 00:04:37,632
Don't know what it means.

80
00:04:38,312 --> 00:04:39,151
To be honest,

81
00:04:39,192 --> 00:04:42,151
General Xu Chengfeng
has entrusted us to escort valuables

82
00:04:42,831 --> 00:04:44,231
and has provided us with a signal flare,

83
00:04:44,271 --> 00:04:45,791
saying if there is any trouble,

84
00:04:45,791 --> 00:04:47,231
we could summon him at any time.

85
00:04:48,112 --> 00:04:50,591
Shen Danqing, how dare you

86
00:04:50,591 --> 00:04:51,471
threaten us here!

87
00:04:51,872 --> 00:04:53,271
I can report this to the official.

88
00:04:53,432 --> 00:04:53,952
Go ahead.

89
00:04:54,992 --> 00:04:57,271
But didn't you tell me?

90
00:04:57,552 --> 00:04:59,351
Who would know what happens

91
00:05:00,952 --> 00:05:02,271
in the Luo's Residence?

92
00:05:02,552 --> 00:05:03,151
You!

93
00:05:03,552 --> 00:05:05,752
Oh, if next time
there's such a good thing,

94
00:05:06,231 --> 00:05:07,591
remember to notify me in advance.

95
00:05:11,752 --> 00:05:12,471
Medical fee.

96
00:05:20,591 --> 00:05:21,831
You!

97
00:05:23,112 --> 00:05:24,151
Mother.

98
00:05:29,031 --> 00:05:30,312
You just wait and see.

99
00:05:32,552 --> 00:05:34,632
I didn't expect the Luo family
to try to bully us.

100
00:05:35,151 --> 00:05:36,911
Miss, you are so smart.

101
00:05:37,112 --> 00:05:37,952
It's really delighted.

102
00:05:38,192 --> 00:05:39,672
At that time, you quietly told me

103
00:05:39,711 --> 00:05:40,591
to buy some fireworks,

104
00:05:40,952 --> 00:05:42,992
and said to light them up
once seeing the Luo's people.

105
00:05:43,391 --> 00:05:46,112
I was so confused.

106
00:05:46,351 --> 00:05:47,231
So you had

107
00:05:47,391 --> 00:05:49,312
such a well-thought-out plan.

108
00:05:49,512 --> 00:05:50,992
After you recovered from the illness,

109
00:05:51,072 --> 00:05:51,952
you became more imposing.

110
00:05:53,872 --> 00:05:54,512
Young Master.

111
00:06:04,952 --> 00:06:05,911
Although they are not aware,

112
00:06:06,271 --> 00:06:07,151
don't try to deceive me.

113
00:06:07,831 --> 00:06:08,632
You went to Luo Residence

114
00:06:08,711 --> 00:06:10,271
not for the business.

115
00:06:10,736 --> 00:06:11,408
Right?

116
00:06:17,031 --> 00:06:18,312
I stole the token

117
00:06:19,271 --> 00:06:20,151
and made the fake command.

118
00:06:22,112 --> 00:06:23,552
It is all my fault.

119
00:06:24,312 --> 00:06:26,151
What exactly happened
at the Luo Residence today?

120
00:06:26,831 --> 00:06:27,711
Tell me everything

121
00:06:28,351 --> 00:06:29,711
in detail.

122
00:06:32,752 --> 00:06:33,512
You're right.

123
00:06:34,432 --> 00:06:35,072
I went there

124
00:06:35,072 --> 00:06:36,632
not for the business.

125
00:06:37,632 --> 00:06:39,312
I knew they wanted to ship out
distiller's yeast.

126
00:06:40,351 --> 00:06:42,192
And this is the perfect time for me.

127
00:06:43,072 --> 00:06:44,552
I had hidden phosphorus powder
in advance,

128
00:06:45,151 --> 00:06:46,552
and sprinkled the powder out

129
00:06:47,672 --> 00:06:49,231
to make the candles
in the ancestral hall explode

130
00:06:51,752 --> 00:06:53,391
while offering incense to my father.

131
00:06:58,992 --> 00:07:00,432
(Ms. Zhou,
Luo Shuangshuang and Luo Jizhou)

132
00:07:00,911 --> 00:07:02,872
(were bound to be scared out of guilt.)

133
00:07:04,711 --> 00:07:05,632
What's going on here?

134
00:07:06,112 --> 00:07:06,711
Mr. Lin.

135
00:07:06,992 --> 00:07:07,512
These are

136
00:07:07,512 --> 00:07:08,952
part of the distiller's yeast.

137
00:07:09,391 --> 00:07:10,192
There's more over there.

138
00:07:10,672 --> 00:07:11,911
(Not only so.)

139
00:07:12,192 --> 00:07:14,151
(I had Mr. Qin sprinkle
some lime into each jar)

140
00:07:14,432 --> 00:07:17,072
(as he checked the distiller's yeast.)

141
00:07:17,992 --> 00:07:19,231
Lime generates heat,

142
00:07:20,312 --> 00:07:21,831
which can speed up the fermentation.

143
00:07:22,992 --> 00:07:23,791
If it ferments too much,

144
00:07:24,672 --> 00:07:26,151
it will produce
a red substance of spoilage.

145
00:07:26,872 --> 00:07:28,151
If the fermentation is sufficient,

146
00:07:28,591 --> 00:07:30,672
the heat generated will burst the jar.

147
00:07:31,512 --> 00:07:32,791
Ms. Zhou and Luo Shuangshuang

148
00:07:32,831 --> 00:07:34,192
don't know much about winemaking,

149
00:07:34,512 --> 00:07:35,591
so they'd never figure out why.

150
00:07:37,072 --> 00:07:39,031
And Luo Jizhou,
having done something evil,

151
00:07:39,711 --> 00:07:41,591
couldn't remember anything in shock.

152
00:07:41,591 --> 00:07:43,231
Do you know how dangerous this is?

153
00:07:43,831 --> 00:07:44,831
You can get away with it

154
00:07:44,831 --> 00:07:46,112
out of luck this time.

155
00:07:46,512 --> 00:07:48,391
You might get caught next time.

156
00:07:48,992 --> 00:07:50,711
Even if you don't get caught
by the Luo family,

157
00:07:51,072 --> 00:07:52,471
they might target the Shen family.

158
00:07:52,672 --> 00:07:54,312
But my face has completely changed,

159
00:07:54,471 --> 00:07:55,728
and my voice changed slightly.

160
00:07:55,728 --> 00:07:56,312
And...

161
00:07:56,312 --> 00:07:57,231
Enough.

162
00:07:57,831 --> 00:07:59,791
Why is your obsession so deep?

163
00:08:00,672 --> 00:08:02,112
You broke into the Luo family

164
00:08:02,391 --> 00:08:04,031
with Mr. Qin,

165
00:08:04,432 --> 00:08:05,312
but how can you ensure

166
00:08:05,312 --> 00:08:06,632
the two of you could get out of it?

167
00:08:07,192 --> 00:08:08,791
You led the escorts
of the Shen Escort Agency

168
00:08:08,911 --> 00:08:11,072
to fool the Luo family,

169
00:08:11,432 --> 00:08:12,591
but how can you ensure

170
00:08:12,632 --> 00:08:13,432
they won't

171
00:08:13,432 --> 00:08:14,952
revenge us?

172
00:08:21,072 --> 00:08:21,632
Exactly.

173
00:08:23,312 --> 00:08:23,952
I admit.

174
00:08:25,952 --> 00:08:27,831
I survive to revenge.

175
00:08:29,391 --> 00:08:30,591
But please trust me.

176
00:08:31,591 --> 00:08:33,312
I have prepared carefully.

177
00:08:34,471 --> 00:08:36,471
Even if it costs my life,

178
00:08:38,032 --> 00:08:39,591
I won't drag you

179
00:08:40,711 --> 00:08:41,991
or the entire Shen family down.

180
00:08:45,776 --> 00:08:52,336
♪Back and forth through
the heavy encirclement of fate♪

181
00:08:52,688 --> 00:08:56,276
♪How many can return♪

182
00:08:57,952 --> 00:08:59,072
What are you...

183
00:09:01,471 --> 00:09:02,272
Nothing.

184
00:09:04,072 --> 00:09:05,392
I came to tell you

185
00:09:05,871 --> 00:09:07,511
Mr. Qin sent the ginseng

186
00:09:07,591 --> 00:09:10,672
that Miss Shen bought to Master.

187
00:09:12,751 --> 00:09:14,192
(So she heard it)

188
00:09:15,432 --> 00:09:16,552
(and remembered it all?)

189
00:09:20,751 --> 00:09:21,672
Miss.

190
00:09:25,871 --> 00:09:28,192
Just now, Young Master
was a bit impulsive.

191
00:09:28,591 --> 00:09:29,591
Please forgive him.

192
00:09:29,871 --> 00:09:30,751
It's my fault.

193
00:09:31,312 --> 00:09:32,471
I really did this

194
00:09:33,072 --> 00:09:34,072
wrong.

195
00:09:34,432 --> 00:09:35,672
I acted without telling him,

196
00:09:35,871 --> 00:09:36,792
causing him to worry.

197
00:09:37,552 --> 00:09:38,831
Let me tell you.

198
00:09:39,792 --> 00:09:41,991
He really cares about
the safety of the Shen family.

199
00:09:42,831 --> 00:09:45,351
Half a year ago, when Young Master
was escorting the imperial valuables,

200
00:09:45,871 --> 00:09:47,231
he heard his sister got poisoned

201
00:09:47,351 --> 00:09:48,991
and needed
a blood transfusion to survive.

202
00:09:49,792 --> 00:09:51,471
He rushed back overnight to save her.

203
00:09:51,751 --> 00:09:53,672
But when he returned at dawn,

204
00:09:54,192 --> 00:09:55,032
he discovered

205
00:09:55,952 --> 00:09:57,831
the imperial valuables got stolen.

206
00:09:59,152 --> 00:10:00,312
Young Master felt ashamed.

207
00:10:00,631 --> 00:10:03,272
From then on, restoring the honor
of Shen has been his mission.

208
00:10:03,831 --> 00:10:06,912
He won't let anything happen
to the Shen family.

209
00:10:11,032 --> 00:10:11,871
I see.

210
00:10:15,672 --> 00:10:17,511
(Looks like the road
to revenge is tough.)

211
00:10:18,111 --> 00:10:19,192
(I need to plan carefully.)

212
00:10:20,552 --> 00:10:21,952
Sorry to let you suffer just now.

213
00:10:22,471 --> 00:10:24,751
This can soothe you, so take it.

214
00:10:28,912 --> 00:10:30,192
I am so useless.

215
00:10:32,032 --> 00:10:33,511
Once I saw the room

216
00:10:33,871 --> 00:10:35,432
full of blood-like distiller's yeast,

217
00:10:36,272 --> 00:10:37,672
it reminded me of that night

218
00:10:38,751 --> 00:10:40,152
when everything was ablaze as well.

219
00:10:41,312 --> 00:10:43,152
Let bygones be bygones.

220
00:10:45,952 --> 00:10:47,711
What should we do now?

221
00:10:48,192 --> 00:10:50,272
The deposit Shen Danqing
tricked away isn't much,

222
00:10:51,072 --> 00:10:52,392
but the ruined distiller's yeast

223
00:10:52,631 --> 00:10:54,032
costs a lot.

224
00:10:54,711 --> 00:10:56,871
If we can't brew
the birthday liquor for Mr. Li,

225
00:10:57,392 --> 00:10:59,351
we will lose a large sum in penalties.

226
00:11:01,552 --> 00:11:03,672
We need a batch of grain
to make the brewing

227
00:11:04,032 --> 00:11:06,032
and sell it to make up
for the losses of the Ganlu Brewery.

228
00:11:06,471 --> 00:11:08,952
The time and location
of this purchase must be confidential.

229
00:11:09,312 --> 00:11:10,751
It's best if only you and I know.

230
00:11:13,111 --> 00:11:15,152
For caution's sake,
you should go personally.

231
00:11:17,192 --> 00:11:19,272
How much do you think today's events

232
00:11:20,032 --> 00:11:21,912
have to do with Shen Danqing?

233
00:11:22,392 --> 00:11:25,032
Why did so many troubles arise
once she came?

234
00:11:25,392 --> 00:11:26,952
Does she know anything?

235
00:11:27,152 --> 00:11:29,192
I've already sent someone
to investigate Shen Danqing.

236
00:11:29,392 --> 00:11:31,711
She was a sick, undead woman.

237
00:11:32,231 --> 00:11:34,231
I don't know what miracle drug
she's taken recently

238
00:11:34,231 --> 00:11:35,111
to come back to life.

239
00:11:35,751 --> 00:11:37,432
The Shen family has never
had any dealings with us.

240
00:11:37,792 --> 00:11:39,672
And there's no way she knows
anything about our family.

241
00:11:43,952 --> 00:11:46,751
Does she really have
a good relationship with General Xu?

242
00:11:47,591 --> 00:11:48,991
If she said something to General Xu

243
00:11:49,032 --> 00:11:50,552
and let him target us,

244
00:11:51,192 --> 00:11:52,351
that would be a hassle.

245
00:11:52,351 --> 00:11:54,192
She has absolutely no relationship
with General Xu.

246
00:11:55,511 --> 00:11:57,711
The armed escorts just
let off the signal flare,

247
00:11:57,711 --> 00:11:59,711
but the people of General's Mansion
did nothing.

248
00:12:00,231 --> 00:12:02,952
She got some inside information

249
00:12:02,952 --> 00:12:05,032
about the General's Mansion
from somewhere,

250
00:12:05,312 --> 00:12:07,871
and tried to take advantage of us.

251
00:12:08,072 --> 00:12:09,312
I will not let her off.

252
00:12:10,111 --> 00:12:11,152
Take the medicine.

253
00:12:24,871 --> 00:12:26,552
- Good.
- Great.

254
00:12:26,871 --> 00:12:27,511
Amazing.

255
00:12:27,511 --> 00:12:28,912
Even General Xu,
the so-called God of War,

256
00:12:29,072 --> 00:12:29,952
is no match for you.

257
00:12:31,072 --> 00:12:31,831
No.

258
00:12:32,312 --> 00:12:34,072
Speaking of the demeanor and manner,

259
00:12:34,312 --> 00:12:35,871
our second leader is better.

260
00:12:36,080 --> 00:12:36,631
Big bro.

261
00:12:36,631 --> 00:12:37,232
Thank you.

262
00:12:37,312 --> 00:12:37,904
Big bro.

263
00:12:38,231 --> 00:12:38,751
Goods are here.

264
00:12:39,312 --> 00:12:39,856
Okay.

265
00:12:40,080 --> 00:12:40,672
Let's go.

266
00:12:40,831 --> 00:12:42,152
- Let's go.
- Let's go.

267
00:12:46,552 --> 00:12:47,471
These past days,

268
00:12:48,072 --> 00:12:50,152
we've scouted all the strongholds
around Liao City,

269
00:12:50,672 --> 00:12:53,072
ruling out all female bandits' suspicion
who might hijack the imperial valuables,

270
00:12:53,312 --> 00:12:54,111
except

271
00:12:54,111 --> 00:12:55,631
the sister of this second leader.

272
00:12:56,192 --> 00:12:56,991
She's the only

273
00:12:57,111 --> 00:12:58,511
female bandit who never shows up.

274
00:12:58,952 --> 00:12:59,991
I'll ask him more about her.

275
00:13:02,952 --> 00:13:04,272
If you follow my strategy,

276
00:13:04,552 --> 00:13:05,991
you will surely unite

277
00:13:05,991 --> 00:13:07,871
all the strongholds of Liao City

278
00:13:08,672 --> 00:13:11,591
and be the king of the bandits.

279
00:13:12,272 --> 00:13:12,831
Bro.

